Suggested Tools
======================

1. **Paper Size Differentiator**: [Diferenciador](https://www.diferenciador.com/tamanos-de-papel-carta-oficio-letter-legal-tabloide) - A tool to specify different paper sizes, providing information on formats like letter, legal, and tabloid.

2. **Color Palette**: [Color Hunt](https://colorhunt.co) offers pre-designed color palettes, and [HTML Color Codes](https://htmlcolorcodes.com) provides color codes in hexadecimal and tools to explore and select colors.

3. **Image Editor Tool**: [PekoStep Alpha Channel Tool](https://www.peko-step.com/es/tool/alphachannel.html) - An online tool for editing images and working with alpha channels, useful for manipulating image transparency.

4. **RML (Report Markup Language) Guide**: [RML2PDF User Guide](https://www.reportlab.com/docs/rml2pdf-userguide.pdf) - The official guide to RML that provides detailed information on how to use the language to generate reports in PDF format.

5. **Django Documentation**: [Django Templates Language](https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/4.0/ref/templates/language) - Django documentation that offers information about the Django template language.
